    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paper money issued as legal tender by specified national banks; also, certain paper currency of the United States issued between 1863 and 1935.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
